              "Wait, checking arithmetic: $2u+3v=1.3 \\times 4 \\Rightarrow 8u+12v=5.2$. $5u-4v=-0.1 \\times 3 \\Rightarrow 15u-12v=-0.3$. $23u = 4.9$. Let's re-verify: $u = 0.2$",
              "Correction: $2(0.2) + 3v = 1.3 \\Rightarrow 0.4 + 3v = 1.3 \\Rightarrow 3v = 0.9 \\Rightarrow v = 0.3$."
