            "derivation": "$2u + 3v = 1.3 \\quad (i) \\\\ 5u - 4v = -0.1 \\quad (ii) \\\\ 8u + 12v = 5.2 \\\\ 15u - 12v = -0.3 \\\\ 23u = 4.9 \\Rightarrow u = 4.9 / 23 \\approx 0.213$."
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "iii",
          "type": "vsa",
          "question": "Find the value of the resistance $R_1$.",
          "answer": "$R_1 = 5 \\Omega$",
          "solution": {
            "steps": [
              "Since $u = \\frac{1}{R_1}$, $R_1 = \\frac{1}{u}$.",
